FBIS3-56859 "drsov014_b_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Boris Fedorov Confirmed as Finance Minister LD1901230094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 2207 GMT 19 Jan 94 LD1901230094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] To start this bulletin here is some information from the Russian prime minister's press service. After two days' lack of clarity the new skeleton of the government was announced today. So, Oleg Soskovets is first deputy prime minister and Aleksandr Zaveryukha, Anatoliy Chubays, and Yuriy Yarov are deputy prime ministers. Boris Fedorov has been confirmed as finance minister.
